These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
City: miami, paris, rome, venice, san-francisco, berlin, edinburgh
The people have 7 different hobbies: writing, collecting, camping, board-games, skydiving, hiking, filmmaking
 1. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person traveling to venice##1
 3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 5. the person traveling to rome is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 8. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
11. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| City           | san-francisco | venice | paris | rome | miami | berlin | edinburgh |
| Hobby   | writing    | skydiving   | board-games      | hiking | camping    | collecting    | filmmaking         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, bolivar, game, tiparillo, pall-mall, siglo, davidoff
The people have 7 different hobbies: woodworking, fishing, reading, puzzles, baking, chess, gardening
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 2. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
 4. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 6. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the game-smoker##1
10. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Cigar          | bongani | bolivar | pall-mall | tiparillo | siglo | davidoff | game |
| Hobby   | fishing      | reading   | puzzles   | baking      | woodworking       | gardening       | chess     |

