.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
7 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, whist, domino, bridge, poker, go
The people have 7 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, chess, filmmaking, baking, photography, cooking
 1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 2. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person playing go##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person playing bridge##1
 6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 9. the person playing poker is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in the middle##1
12. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Game   | scrabble | bridge     | whist  | poker       | backgammon       | go  | domino   |
| Hobby    | photography  | card-games | cooking | filmmaking | gardening | chess | baking |

