.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, hot-chocolate, mirinda, sprite, juice, water
7 different games are played: billiard, chess, poker, bridge, scrabble, domino, snooker
 1. the person drinking sprite is the person playing chess##1
 2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 3. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing poker is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person playing scrabble##1
10. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
11. the person playing snooker is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | juice    | water     | mirinda     | hot-chocolate      | fanta | sprite      | coffee     |
| Game   | bridge | poker | domino | scrabble | snooker | chess | billiard |

