.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, iced-tea, almond-milk, juice, mirinda, coffee, lemonade
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, begonia, rose, lily, poppy, zinnia, aconite
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who growsaconite##1
 2. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 3. the person who growszinnia is in the middle##1
 4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 5. the person who growspoppy is the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 7. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | almond-milk | coffee     | juice | lemonade | mirinda | soy-milk |
| Flower     | aconite   | rose    | poppy | zinnia     | amaryllis         | lily     | begonia        |

