.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: water-polo, parkour, swimming, rugby, golf, rowing, sailing
There 7 different types of food: mango, nectarine, radish, pear, eggplant, pepper, papaya
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person eating pear##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person eating mango##1
 3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
 4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 5. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
10. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Sport    | swimming | rowing   | water-polo | rugby | sailing  | golf | parkour |
| Food   | pear   | eggplant | mango | pepper     | nectarine | papaya | radish   |

