.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: orange, lavender, mauve, green, amber, light-blue, emerald
There 7 different types of food: grapes, pear, watermelon, spinach, cabbage, corn, carrot
 1. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person eating pear##1
 2. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 3. the person who likes emerald is the person eating spinach##1
 4. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
 5. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
 6. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 7. the person eating grapes is the person who likes mauve##1
 8. the person who likes amber is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
10. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Color   | orange  | emerald | green | amber | light-blue     | lavender | mauve |
| Food     | corn | spinach      | carrot | watermelon    | cabbage | pear   | grapes  |

