 5. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 7. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 8. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
