The people's birthday is in 7 different months: march, august, november, april, october, september, december
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |    7     |
